{"tid":938983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咁凍 點沖涼啊！","createTime":"2018-12-12T17:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T20:19:05.000Z","uid":160537,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fb2815c82f74ab3e6128502621c4552fbbd8f165","tid":938983,"uid":160537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:31:37.000Z","msg":"沖涼之前明明凍到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知點解一除晒衫就感受唔到凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重好老定咁開水喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開水喉就嚟料<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淋邊度就剩係暖邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n沖涼沖到彈吓彈吓咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n閂水搽鹼液個陣 成身好似石化咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能因為熱脹冷縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n碌鳩由31.5cm 縮到得返20cm 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係沖完涼先暖返啲 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0426e4e82364e7cbc3179d05cd4180dda38fcb11","tid":938983,"uid":199718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:32:45.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"2a85611a50206e2b4db081172fb6c8fe9ba7ccad","tid":938983,"uid":49055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:36:01.000Z","msg":"原來有人會沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79679bb51612ae893ea7ec7946a1b73d79b5f148","tid":938983,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T20:19:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}